1.0.2.name: wordpress/feedgeorge-augmented-reality-plugin
1.0.2.description:
To help users in creating augmented reality (AR) content via WordPress CMS, we introduce you Feedgeorge Augmented Reality Plugin (FGARP). This plugin supports only Geolocation and Layar Vision in Layar mobile browser.

= With this plugin, WordPress users are able to: a) create Layar Geolocation content. b) create Layar Vision content. c) embed map for AR geopoint
